OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy start, with a
OL,6,Ffew outbreaks of rain. Perhaps the odd
OL,7,Fwarm sunnier spell developing early
OL,8,Fafternoon, along with isolated
OL,9,Fshowers. A band of heavy rain and
OL,10,Fgusty winds then moves east later,
OL,11,Ffollowed by further isolated showers.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny rain or showers soon
OL,14,Fclearing into the evening with clear
OL,15,Fspells developing. Cloud then thickens
OL,16,Fagain from the west after midnight,
OL,17,Fwith further showers possible. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
