OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FBreezy start with a mixture
OL,6,Fof sunny spells and showers,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy. Winds will ease
OL,8,Fthrough the day, with showers also
OL,9,Ffading into the evening. Cooler than
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLight
OL,13,Frain clearing Friday morning. Staying
OL,14,Fcloudy before further rain,
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy spreads east later
OL,16,Fin the day. Sunny spells and showers
OL,17,FSaturday. Drier, and sunnier with
OL,18,Fwinds easing Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
